Package: saturate
Title: Qualitative Text Coding with DuckDB and Shiny
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Thomas", "Wood", email = "thomaswood1994@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A modern replacement for RQDA. Create and manage qualitative
    coding projects backed by DuckDB, annotate text passages interactively
    via a Shiny GUI, and retrieve coded segments as tidy tibbles.
